        <source>utlUpdateTermAreaHazDetails(_pxyHazDetails : CM_TerminalAreaHazDetails;	_passport : CM_Passport input);
//
// Purpose:			
//
// Parameters:			
//
// Return Value:		
//
// Changed On	By			Reason
// ----------	--------	-----------------------------------------------------
// 23/11/2016	cnwdap1		Initial creation TFS 2844 STWR Hazardous Details Enhancements
//
